'''Søren Balling Engelsen''', Ph.D. (1992), is a Danish chemist, who is active in the fields of [[analytical chemistry]] and [[food science]]; he is a professor of the [[University of Copenhagen]] (UCPH) since 2004.<ref>UCPH, 2018</ref>

