'''''Y Gwyddonydd''''' ("The Scientist") was a [[Welsh-language]] [[magazine]] containing articles, reviews, and news items on [[science|scientific]] topics. It was published between 1963 and 1996 by the [[University of Wales Press]].

The magazine has been digitized by the [[National Library of Wales#Welsh Journals Online|Welsh Journals Online]] project at the [[National Library of Wales]].

